        <br><br>
        <p>After the popular uprising against dictatorship in Haiti in 1986, Dodard’s style completely changed from fluid water imagery to much stronger strokes of black and white inks. Dodard is a diverse artist whose body of work also includes metalwork, large sculptures and jewelry.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid__item large--one-third text-center">
